div.div:
Add custom widgets for navigation and menu components
- Introduced HesMenu class for a custom menu implementation with animation and styling features. - Added HesNavigationBar class to manage navigation elements, including user cards and navigation buttons. - Implemented HesText class for styled text display with support for icons and various text styles. - Created HesToolButton class for a customizable tool button with menu integration and animation effects. - Enhanced interaction and visual feedback for navigation and menu components.

feat: Implement HesAppBarPrivate class with button functionalities and system menu support
- Added HesAppBarPrivate class to manage app bar functionalities including minimize, maximize, close, and stay on top buttons. - Implemented system menu display for Windows with DPI scaling. - Added cursor update logic based on window edges for resizing. - Introduced theme mode change handling for light and dark themes. - Created layout management for app bar components. - Added Q_DECLARE_FLAGS documentation for better understanding of flag handling in Qt.

Add Windows color console sink to spdlog
- Introduced `wincolor_sink` and its associated header and implementation files to support colored logging in Windows console applications. - Implemented `wincolor_stdout_sink` and `wincolor_stderr_sink` for standard output and error streams. - Enhanced the spdlog library to include the new sinks and updated the necessary headers. - Added stopwatch functionality for measuring elapsed time in logging. - Updated logging mechanism in `HesLogPrivate` to handle message logging with timestamps and context information. - Implemented file logging capabilities with options for log file naming and path configuration.

Refactor HesWidgetsDesign components and add example application
- Updated HesWinShadowHelper to improve DWM API initialization and error handling. - Modified Singleton.h to use raw pointers instead of unique_ptr for instance management. - Added resource file for including custom font (HesAwesome.ttf). - Enhanced common_defs.h for better compatibility with Qt versions. - Cleaned up stdafx.h by removing Vulkan-related code and added a dedicated DisableVulkan.cmake script. - Created a new example application (HesWidgetsDesignExample) to demonstrate the usage of HesApplication and HesTheme. - Implemented a simple test application with UI for testing various features of HesWidgetsDesign. - Removed outdated build scripts (build.bat and build.sh) to streamline the build process. - Updated CMakeLists.txt to include necessary directories and resources for the example application.
